DIMENSION_DIALOG_TEXT_1: Here you'll be able to assign technical skills to your team's roles.
DIMENSION_DIALOG_TEXT_2: This will allow us to define skills and knowledge in order to build the career plan for each profile.
DIMENSION_DIALOG_TEXT_3: In Groowcity, we help you to define in a very specific way your entire team, with which we generate appreciations tailormade for you. The skills we offer are the most used in the market and we organize them so that you can build your roles under a standard so that we all understand each other
DIMENSION_DIALOG_TEXT_4: In case you need a skill you don't see, you can click here to request it and we will give it to you as soon as possible.
Te invitamos a conocer los Roles: We invite you to know the roles
ROLE_DIALOG_TEXT_1: In Groowcity, roles are fundamental and it is important for you to know that the assignment of roles in a work team basically depends on the technical-professional-human skills of each collaborator, which are the main reason why you have chosen to be part of your team.
ROLE_DIALOG_TEXT_2: Once you have identified the roles of your team, you must send the assigned roles of each person in your area to our Groowcity team, we will upload them to the platform.
ROLE_DIALOG_TEXT_3: Once the Roles are loaded, you must assign maturity levels to each role, this will allow you to visualize the path they are acquiring. The maturity levels are the hierarchical structure you want to give to the growth of the roles, we give you some examples: Junior, Medium and Senior.
ROLE_DIALOG_TEXT_4: From here you will be able to review all the assigned roles and the maturity level of each one.
CAREERS_DIALOG_TEXT_1: In the careers module you will be able to create and maintain the learning path that will generate goals for your teams.
CAREERS_DIALOG_TEXT_2: This will allow the growth of your team, enhance skills and have the visualization of knowledge of each role.
CAREERS_DIALOG_TEXT_3: When creating a career to an assigned role, you will need to add career elements which are associated to technical knowledge linked to the particular career.
CAREERS_DIALOG_TEXT_4: From the Career Plan module you will be able to find a map that allows you to visualize the careers assigned to each role and a map of the progress and development of each professional profile.
CAREERS_ELEMS_DIALOG_TEXT_1: In this module you will be able to create and maintain career elements for your teams' careers' paths.
CAREERS_ELEMS_DIALOG_TEXT_2: Career elements are a set of specific topics that are aligned to a career according to the assigned role.
CAREERS_ELEMS_DIALOG_TEXT_3: To create career elements it is necessary to be clear about the skills that were assigned to a role.
CAREERS_ELEMS_DIALOG_TEXT_4: In the career elements container provided by Groowcity you will be able to edit the contents of your career elements integrating study material (Multimedia) and test questions.
MULTIMEDIA_DIALOG_TEXT_1: In this maintainer you can upload and update support material.
MULTIMEDIA_DIALOG_TEXT_2: Here, you can add everything from course links, to infographics, video tutorials, articles, forum posts, etc.
MULTIMEDIA_DIALOG_TEXT_3: The material you will find in this section will be categorized by tags (tags) that will allow you to quickly access the information you are looking for.
MULTIMEDIA_DIALOG_TEXT_4: It's important that you upload your academic multimedia because this will allow to further refine your career elements.
MULTIMEDIA_DIALOG_TEXT_5: At Groowcity we want to help you enhance the collaboration of knowledge and the development of each Role.
USERS_DIALOG_TEXT_1: Let's be social! Sending and receiving invitations from different teams (or communities) strengthens collaboration.
USERS_DIALOG_TEXT_2: From here you can check who are the users that belong to your team and the assigned role, send invitations to the participants you want and check the status of these invitations.
USERS_DIALOG_TEXT_3: That's not all, from the maintainer you can edit the participation of any member, grant permissions to users and assign careers, this will allow you to increase the development of each role or view the progress percentage.
USERS_DIALOG_TEXT_4: Build your team up! In this section you will be able to build a team by selecting from our available talented Collaborators.
USERS_DIALOG_TEXT_5: Use the browser to filter among our Colaborators based on the technologies or requirements you need for your project.
TEAMS_DIALOG_TEXT_1: At Groowcity we believe that collaborative work is essential, even more so if we can share knowledge in the same way.
TEAMS_DIALOG_TEXT_2: From the team maintainer you can create teams with common goals and objectives, with assigned users and leaders. In addition, you can get a clear view of all the teams you create and participate in.
DIALOG_QUESTION_MANTAINER_TITLE: Questions: How much do we know?
QUESTIONS_DIALOG_TEXT_1: From this maintainer, you will be able to create questions in text format, allowing you to insert elements or links and tables.
QUESTIONS_DIALOG_TEXT_2: You need to know what you are looking for from a particular profile and create specific technical questions, this will allow you to identify the knowledge of the roles that make up your team, what is their level of maturity and what are the objectives that they should integrate into their career elements.
QUESTIONS_DIALOG_TEXT_3: These knowledge questions are associated with an ability or tags (label). You can also view, edit and delete all the questions generated.
USER_FEEDBACK_DIALOG_TEXT_1: Feedback from colleagues and customers alike is of vital importance to our Colaborators and teams.
USER_FEEDBACK_DIALOG_TEXT_2: Please consider that the information you submit in this section will be shared with the whole Collaborators community, so we appreciate that anything you submit is always from a constructive point of view.
USER_FEEDBACK_DIALOG_TEXT_3: As Clever community, we appeal to always maintain our Cooltura values and our professionalism.
USER_FEEDBACK_DIALOG_TEXT_4:
You can use the following questions as a guide:
- What are the Clever's strengths or values?
- What would you recommend the Clever to improve?
- How satisfied are you with the Clever's performance?
SKILL_DIALOG_TEXT_1: Defining the set of technical skills to create a role is key, since these are the skills we look for in professionals to perform a specific position.
